title: Silver Surfer v5 01-14 (2003-2004|Digital|AnPymGold-Empire)
description: This is the full run of Silver Surfer v5, by Stacy Weiss and Dan Charlton with art by Lan Medina and others. After the one-shot v2, the 146-issue lengthy ongoing v3 and the two-issue v4 (known as "Parable"), this series was distinctly designed as two parts - the six issue "Communion" arc and the eight issue "Revelation" arc. All 14 issues are included here, in digital editions thanks to AnPymGold-Empire. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
